            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Planets can be found anywhere in space...</h1>
            <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
                <p class="lead mb-4 ">Planets can be part of a galaxy or a solar system, you now like humans are part of some community, isn't that great?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 30vh;">
